"tag-public-trust-al-amanah","tag-trade-al-tijarah","tag-umar-ibn-al-khattab","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2CC","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33902,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/09\/prohibition-divorcing-menstruation\/","url_meta":{"origin":10082,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Talaq: Prohibition of divorcing women during menstruation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: He divorced his wife in the time of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while she menstruating. Umar ibn al-Khattab asked the Prophet about that and he said, \u201cOrder him to return her. Let him leave her alone until she becomes pure, then\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25668,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/28\/shurut-nikah-wajib-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":10082,"position":1},"title":"Umar on Nikah: Muslims uphold conditions in marriage contracts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn Ghanm reported: I was sitting closely with Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him. A man said, \u201cO commander of the faithful, I married this woman and I accepted her condition that she would keep her house. I have settled my affairs such that I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/cat