\/umar-inbreeding-marriage-cousins\/","url_meta":{"origin":10082,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Inbreeding: Do not to marry within bloodlines, close cousins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Mulaykah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to the house of Al-Sa\u2019ib, \u201cYou have become frail, so marry intelligent people unrelated to you.\u201d Al-Shafi\u2019i said, \u201cWhenever the people of a household do not allow their women to marry men outside of their line,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25924,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/15\/secret-marraige-zina\/","url_meta":{"origin":10082,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Zina: Secret marriage is a type of adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Zubayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, was presented with a marriage which no one had witnessed but one man and one woman. Umar said, \u201cThis is a secret marriage and I do not permit it. If I had known of it beforehand, I would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10082","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"h